       Name: Cloak:reflection
       Kind: Spell
     Target: TAR_CHAR_DEFENSIVE
   Position: POS_STANDING
   Min Mana: 500
 Wait Beats: 12
 Can Learn: FALSE
Noun Damage: None
   Wear-Off: @@NThe @@lc@@el@@ro@@ya@@ak@@N around your body fades.
Acquisition:
   - Not learnable by player classes.
Description:
   Cloak:reflection surrounds the caster in a shimmering, multi-hued cloak
   that has a chance to reflect offensive spells back at the original caster.
   When a spell hits the caster, there is a (pseudo_level - 70) percent
   chance that the cloak will reflect the spell, dealing its full damage back
   to the attacker instead.

   The cloak only triggers against offensive targeted spells
   (TAR_CHAR_OFFENSIVE) and does not activate if the caster is targeting
   themselves. Reflected spells deal their original damage to the attacker.

   Duration scales with pseudo-level (pseudo_level / 8 rounds).
*******************************************************************************
